青蟳屬有四品種<ref name="Ng">{{cite journal |journal=Raffles Bulletin of Zoology |year=2008 |volume=17 |pages=1–286 |title=Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant Brachyuran crabs of the world |author=Peter K. L. Ng, Danièle Guinot & Peter J. F. Davie |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |access-date=2011-01-25 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606061453/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中最常見為[[锯缘青蟹|锯缘青蟹]]。青蟳屬常見於[[印度洋-太平洋海域|印度洋-太平洋海域]]。<ref>{{cite journal |journal=Asian Fisheries Science |volume=14 |year=2001 |pages=101–111 |title=Ecology and management of mud crab ''Scylla'' spp. |author=L. Le Vay |url=http://www.asianfisheriessociety.org/modules/wfdownloads/visit.php?cid=17&lid=456 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725020826/http://www.asianfisheriessociety.org/modules/wfdownloads/visit.php?cid=17&lid=456 |archivedate=2011-07-25 }}</ref>

